intent.user_query: Which product has the highest return rate (based on service tickets)?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductName, COUNT(st.TicketID) AS TotalTickets FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets st JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON st.ProductID = p.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductName ORDER BY TotalTickets DESC LIMIT 1;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductName, COUNT(st.TicketID) AS TotalTickets FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets st JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON st.ProductID = p.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductName ORDER BY TotalTickets DESC LIMIT 1;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
